        public static int menu(java.util.Scanner kb)
        menu method for testing your linked list
        1) Print the List
        2) Create a BoxCar and append the specified element to the end of this list.
        3) addAll(index, array)
        4) Read an index and get the data at that index
        5) getLast
        6) remove
        7) removeIndex
        8) removeLast
        9) toArray
        10) clear the list
        11) Print the size of the list
        You must ensure the value entered in within range

        Returns:
        int The choice
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if kb is null
